1: Yes the audible vibrations are the deaths of a -1 instance.

2: The numbers we're looking at are, over a 50 year period about 13 million dead instances from hitting the cover.

3: This is to ensure that the site director, who has to observe the procedures, and likely could tell that these are not brainless beasts, isn't contaminated by that information. In this case, the director deleted the note from the last director, didn't do any of the digging or investigation the old site directed hoped he would, and instead just took his amnestic treatment(which is what happens when you click ).







